data.description: Amazing Backyard Oasis!!!    A Tropical paradise awaits. This stunning heated POOL & SPA HOME is located in the desired South West Cape Coral area. This 3 bed, 2 bath with a den and partially finished 2 car garage property is High and Dry. Never had water damage or flooding! Enter this backyard oasis with plenty of privacy from the lush Areca palms that surround the pool deck and the large custom patio area perfect for entertaining.  Many new appliances, new pool heater and pool equipment, the entire pool and spa have been resurfaced, a new roof and SOLAR PANELS, water heater, paint inside and out and much more. This is a must see.
